    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>harissa mayo</strong></p>",
